snippet.title: Florida Police Killed THREE Black Girls and are Covering it up!

localized.description:
Comrades please don't believe the lies! These pigs murdered these three African girls here in St. Petersburg Florida where I live! The police are falsifying documents making these girls look like criminals!

The police lied and said they tried to save the girls! The Deputies that lied received awards, bonuses, and called heroes in the local news paper. A dash cam video leaked of the SAME DEPUTIES standing there and laughing while the girls drowned and screamed for 20 minutes! The girls did not steal a car!

They were abducted by a 36 year old man that none of the parents even knew of! When the man got out the car he accidentally left the keys and the girls drove off scared at 4am! The police chased them with their lights off!! Then the details get fuzzy!

We see when the car was picked up out the water there is damage at the back of the car that the police won't even acknowledge! Who hit the back of the car? We know it's the pigs! The same pigs that murder our children! The same pigs that are responsible for mass incarceration! The same pigs that get away with murder time and time again!

Please do not believe the media they are only reporting what the murdering pigs are telling them!

Sheriff Bob is a freaking maniac who terrorizes the black community and is responsible for the unarmed deaths of dozens of Africans in St. Pete FL! He is known here locally as "KILLER BOB"!

Please don't believe the lies!

Get the truth from the local Black Power News Paper at TheBurningSpear.com The Uhuru Movement is leading the fight for these three beautiful girls!

We are holding vigils protests marches and walk outs and the mothers are ready to fight with us all the way! UHURU!
